      <div type="commentary" xml:lang="eng">
	<p>This edition is reedited on the basis of <ref target="bibl:Seshadri1972">Seshadri’s</ref> rubbing (plate 22) and photographs of the object in the State Museum, Gulbarga.</p>
	<p>The object looks like a memorial-stone to me, but Nagaraja Rao thought that it recorded a donation by Rāmaśrī.</p>
